title: 02/23/22 DPS Hour 1 - Rob Parker & Ben Maller Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 02/23/22 DPS Hour 1 - Rob Parker & Ben Maller Guest Hosting
description:
Rob Parker and Ben Maller, filling in for Dan, debate whether or not Aaron Rodgers is being a drama queen by dragging on the announcement regarding his football future in Green Bay, argue about how much credit Matthew Stafford actually deserved for winning the Super Bowl for the Los Angeles Rams, discuss whether or not the postgame handshake should be abolished in college basketball, and much more!
